Well....finally working. Before it had always shown: picture unavailable etc. How I made this work: I'm running the note 4 with nova launcher. I use 3 home screens. Therefore I created 3 folders i file manager and put the wallpapers I wanted to use in them. Open live wallpaper then select MP live. Create your screen settings pages (home screen pages). Remember, picture source= picture folder. Use the folders you created for that particular screen. I also used the honeycomb tablet workaround option. Hope this helps.
